<!-- Banner -->
<div class="banner-peetayers" style="background-image: linear-gradient(-225deg, rgba(0,101,168,0.6) 0%, rgba(0,36,61,0.6) 50%), url('<%=image_path "https://source.unsplash.com/collection/865018/1000x300"%>');">
  <div class="banner-peetayers-content">
    <h1>Welcome</h1>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- End Banner -->

<div class="container">
  <div class="body">
    <div class="row">

      <div class="column-1">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-3">
          <div class="polaroid flo">
            <div class="polaroid-img" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.2)), url('<%=image_path "peetayers/bastien.jpg" %>');">
            </div>
            <p class="polaroid-text"><strong>Bastien, 20 ans<strong></p>
            <p class="polaroid-desc">"I know Lille inside out!"</p>
          </div>
          <br>

          <div class="infos">
            <div class="infos-title text-center">
              <p><strong>Information checked</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="infos-content">
              <ul><p><i class="far fa-check-circle"></i> Official ID</p></ul>
              <ul><p><i class="far fa-check-circle"></i> Phone</p></ul>
              <ul><p><i class="far fa-check-circle"></i> Email</p></ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="column-2">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-9">

          <div class="row">
            <div class="space1 text-center">
              <div class="space1-title">
                <h3>Hello, I'm Bastien!</h3>
              </div>
              <div class="space1-content">
                <p>Lille, France ° since 2 years</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="space2">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                <div class="space2-title">
                  <p><strong>Available services</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                <div class="space2-content">
                  <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                      <%= image_tag "flaticon/suitcase.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                      <p>Prepare your trip</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                      <%= image_tag "flaticon/location.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                      <p>Housing services</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                      <%= image_tag "flaticon/medical-history.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                      <p>Help with admins</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                      <%= image_tag "flaticon/chat.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                      <p>Speak local</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                      <%= image_tag "flaticon/cheers.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                      <p>Local tips</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                      <%= image_tag "flaticon/masks.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                      <p>Cultural outings</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                      <%= image_tag "flaticon/football.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                      <p>Play sports</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                      <%= image_tag "flaticon/welcome.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                      <p>Be welcomed</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="space2">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                <div class="space2-title">
                  <p><strong>Languages?</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                <div class="space2-content">
                  <p>French & English</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="space2">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                <div class="space2-title">
                  <p><strong>Why do you like Lille?</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                <div class="space2-content">
                  <p>Une ville très vivante où l'on ne s'ennuie jamais, de plus très étudiante et adaptée pour eux. C'est un carrefour européen entre le nord et le Sud, et sa proximité avec la Belgique en fait un lieu de choix.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="space2">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                <div class="space2-title">
                  <p><strong>Your favorite spots in Lille?</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                <div class="space2-content">
                  <p>Le lobby est un bar du vieux lille avec un large choix de bière et une ambiance Pub anglais super.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="space2">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                <div class="space2-title">
                  <p><strong>Why do you want to become a Peetayer?</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                <div class="space2-content">
                  <p>J'adorerais rencontrer de  nouvelles personnes surtout étrangères pour pouvoir échanger, découvrir des gens et entretenir mon niveau en langues étrangères.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="space2">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                <div class="space2-title">
                  <p><strong>What are your interests?</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                <div class="space2-content">
                  <p>Tennis, volley, théâtre (comédie), musées historiques,  bars, concerts et festivals, dessins, cinéma, série </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="space2">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                <div class="space2-title">
                  <p><strong>What about Bastien?</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                <div class="space2-content">
                  <p>Moi, Bastien, 19 ans, 1m75, en 2e année de médecine à  Lille. Toujours souriant et prêt à rencontrer de nouvelles personnes, les bons plans Lille ça me connait!</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="space2">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                <div class="space2-title">
                  <p><strong>Which countries have you visited?</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                <div class="space2-content">
                  <p>Espagne en vacances, Angleterre en vacances et avec l'école, Belgique pour les vacances.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

